<para><computeroutput>partial record Luthetus.Common.RazorLib.Dimensions.States.AppDimensionState (int Width, int Height, int Left, int Top)</computeroutput></para><para>

<para>The measurements are in pixels (px). This class is in reference to the &quot;browser&quot;, &quot;user agent&quot;, &quot;desktop application which is rendering a webview&quot;, etc... </para>
</para>

<para>When one resizes the application, then IDispatcher.IDispatcher.Dispatch the SetAppDimensionStateAction.</para>

<para>Any part of the application can subscribe to this state, and be notified when a SetAppDimensionStateAction was reduced.</para>

